beddable.*\",\n                    \".*META-INF/native-image/org\\\\.jline/.*\")\n        }\n    }\n    ...\n}\n```\n\n- Refined `ScriptiDefinitionsFromClasspathDiscoverySourceKtTest.kt`\n  - Removed the ASM dependency usage.\n  - Replaced generated-bytecode construction with a small precomputed class byte array.\n  - Added the required `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(...)` handling around the dynamically loaded classpath-directory discovery test, since that path fundamentally relies on runtime class definition from classpath bytes.\n\nI did not run the Gradle command locally, per workflow instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07e37d872963455d016a2a207439c4819596f7cc51b890ea0c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1740, "output": 714, "cacheRead": 92672, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 95126, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781145701609, "responseId": "resp_07e37d872963455d016a2a2066cf948195888cb6dc5c9dc32d"}, "toolResults": []}
